{
  "font_size": 0.4,
  "font_color": "#FFFFFF",
  "background_alpha": 0.5,
  "background_color": "#9C27B0",
  "Stroke": "none",
  "type": "AIsubtitle",
  "lang": "zh",
  "version": "eng-1.2.0-Index-johns-pen-lite",
  "body": [
    {
      "content": "一个充满活力的工作流程可能包含多种不同类型的组件",
      "from": 0.04,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 1,
      "to": 4.26
    },
    {
      "content": "因此，改进不同组件的工具会大不相同",
      "from": 4.26,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 2,
      "to": 8.26
    },
    {
      "content": "但我想与大家分享一些通用模式",
      "from": 8.26,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 3,
      "to": 10.4
    },
    {
      "content": "我发现某些组件可能不基于语言模型",
      "from": 10.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 4,
      "to": 15.11
    },
    {
      "content": "这可能像网络搜索引擎或文本检索组件",
      "from": 15.11,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 5,
      "to": 19.93
    },
    {
      "content": "如果这是你检索增强生成系统的一部分",
      "from": 19.93,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 6,
      "to": 23.34
    },
    {
      "content": "可能需要代码执行功能",
      "from": 23.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 7,
      "to": 24.96
    },
    {
      "content": "或者一个单独训练的机器学习模型",
      "from": 24.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 8,
      "to": 27.58
    },
    {
      "content": "可能是语音识别或图片中人物检测等功能",
      "from": 27.58,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 9,
      "to": 31.2
    },
    {
      "content": "这些非语言模型组件可能有可调参数或超参数",
      "from": 31.2,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 10,
      "to": 37.58
    },
    {
      "content": "对于网络搜索",
      "from": 37.58,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 11,
      "to": 38.36
    },
    {
      "content": "可以调整结果数量等参数",
      "from": 38.36,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 12,
      "to": 40.4
    },
    {
      "content": "或设置网络搜索引擎考虑的时间范围",
      "from": 40.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 13,
      "to": 44.06
    },
    {
      "content": "对于文本检索组件",
      "from": 44.06,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 14,
      "to": 46.48
    },
    {
      "content": "可能改变相似度阈值以确定文本相似性",
      "from": 46.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 15,
      "to": 51.48
    },
    {
      "content": "或调整分块大小",
      "from": 51.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 16,
      "to": 52.74
    },
    {
      "content": "通常检索系统会进行分块处理",
      "from": 52.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 17,
      "to": 55.01
    },
    {
      "content": "将其拆分为更小块以便匹配",
      "from": 55.01,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 18,
      "to": 57.35
    },
    {
      "content": "这些超参数可能适用于人物检测",
      "from": 57.35,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 19,
      "to": 60.93
    },
    {
      "content": "可以调整检测阈值",
      "from": 60.93,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 20,
      "to": 62.98
    },
    {
      "content": "影响其敏感度",
      "from": 62.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 21,
      "to": 64.32
    },
    {
      "content": "以及识别人物的可能性",
      "from": 64.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 22,
      "to": 66.9
    },
    {
      "content": "这会在假阳性和假阴性之间权衡",
      "from": 66.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 23,
      "to": 69.6
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你没有完全理解我刚才提到的超参数细节",
      "from": 69.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 24,
      "to": 72.4
    },
    {
      "content": "不必担心",
      "from": 72.4,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 25,
      "to": 73.14
    },
    {
      "content": "细节并不重要",
      "from": 73.14,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 26,
      "to": 74.48
    },
    {
      "content": "但组件参数通常可调",
      "from": 74.48,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 27,
      "to": 77.5
    },
    {
      "content": "当然，你也可以尝试替换组件",
      "from": 77.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 28,
      "to": 80.78
    },
    {
      "content": "我在自动生成工作流中经常这样做",
      "from": 80.78,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 29,
      "to": 83.42
    },
    {
      "content": "我会切换不同的检索增强生成引擎",
      "from": 83.42,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 30,
      "to": 85.93
    },
    {
      "content": "或更换不同的检索服务提供商等",
      "from": 85.93,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 31,
      "to": 88.15
    },
    {
      "content": "只需测试其他提供商是否因非语言模型组件多样性表现更好",
      "from": 88.15,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 32,
      "to": 94.76
    },
    {
      "content": "我认为改进技术会更多样化且依赖于",
      "from": 94.76,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 33,
      "to": 99.13
    },
    {
      "content": "具体组件的功能，对于语言模型组件",
      "from": 99.13,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 34,
      "to": 103.69
    },
    {
      "content": "这里有一些可考虑的选项",
      "from": 103.69,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 35,
      "to": 105.99
    },
    {
      "content": "其中一个可能是尝试优化你的",
      "from": 105.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 36,
      "to": 108.9
    },
    {
      "content": "或许添加更明确的指令",
      "from": 108.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 37,
      "to": 111.72
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你了解少样本提示法",
      "from": 111.72,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 38,
      "to": 114.14
    },
    {
      "content": "指添加输入和期望输出的具体示例",
      "from": 114.14,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 39,
      "to": 120.52
    },
    {
      "content": "少样本提示",
      "from": 120.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 40,
      "to": 121.96
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以在深度端眼短课程中学习",
      "from": 121.96,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 41,
      "to": 125.229
    },
    {
      "content": "是一种提供示例以",
      "from": 125.229,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 42,
      "to": 128.989
    },
    {
      "content": "帮助生成更优输出的技术",
      "from": 128.989,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 43,
      "to": 132.46
    },
    {
      "content": "或者尝试不同的AI工具",
      "from": 132.46,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 44,
      "to": 136.5
    },
    {
      "content": "套件或其他工具",
      "from": 136.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 45,
      "to": 137.52
    },
    {
      "content": "尝试多种语言模型其实很容易",
      "from": 137.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 46,
      "to": 140.5
    },
    {
      "content": "然后使用评估选择最佳模型",
      "from": 140.5,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 47,
      "to": 144.88
    },
    {
      "content": "如果单步操作对单一模型太复杂",
      "from": 144.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 48,
      "to": 148.66
    },
    {
      "content": "可以考虑将任务分解为更小步骤",
      "from": 148.66,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 49,
      "to": 151.98
    },
    {
      "content": "或拆分为生成步骤和反思步骤",
      "from": 151.98,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 50,
      "to": 155.82
    },
    {
      "content": "但更一般地说",
      "from": 155.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 51,
      "to": 156.54
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你有非常复杂的指令",
      "from": 156.54,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 52,
      "to": 159.43
    },
    {
      "content": "全部在一个步骤内",
      "from": 159.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 53,
      "to": 160.69
    },
    {
      "content": "可能单个模型难以完成所有指令",
      "from": 160.69,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 54,
      "to": 164.02
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以将任务分解为更小的步骤",
      "from": 164.02,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 55,
      "to": 168.04
    },
    {
      "content": "比如两到三次调用以准确执行最后",
      "from": 168.04,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 56,
      "to": 172.44
    },
    {
      "content": "当其他方法不起作用时可以尝试",
      "from": 172.44,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 57,
      "to": 175.1
    },
    {
      "content": "充分考虑微调模型",
      "from": 175.1,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 58,
      "to": 178.6
    },
    {
      "content": "这通常比其他选项复杂得多",
      "from": 178.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 59,
      "to": 181.62
    },
    {
      "content": "在开发时间投入上也会更昂贵",
      "from": 181.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 60,
      "to": 185.9
    },
    {
      "content": "但如果你有可用于微调模型的数据",
      "from": 185.9,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 61,
      "to": 191.57
    },
    {
      "content": "这可能比单纯提示更有效",
      "from": 191.57,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 62,
      "to": 195.29
    },
    {
      "content": "所以我通常在耗尽其他选项后才微调模型",
      "from": 195.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 63,
      "to": 199.65
    },
    {
      "content": "因为微调通常较为复杂",
      "from": 199.65,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 64,
      "to": 202.32
    },
    {
      "content": "但对于应用而言",
      "from": 202.32,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 65,
      "to": 204.62
    },
    {
      "content": "尝试过所有其他方法后",
      "from": 204.62,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 66,
      "to": 205.92
    },
    {
      "content": "如果我仍然处于",
      "from": 205.92,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 67,
      "to": 206.86
    },
    {
      "content": "你知道的",
      "from": 206.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 68,
      "to": 207.22
    },
    {
      "content": "比如达到90%或95%的性能",
      "from": 207.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 69,
      "to": 210.34
    },
    {
      "content": "我需要挤出最后几个百分点的提升",
      "from": 210.34,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 70,
      "to": 213.82
    },
    {
      "content": "有时微调自定义模型是很好的技术",
      "from": 213.82,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 71,
      "to": 217.94
    },
    {
      "content": "我通常只在成熟应用上这样做",
      "from": 217.94,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 72,
      "to": 221.52
    },
    {
      "content": "因为成本很高",
      "from": 221.52,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 73,
      "to": 223.44
    },
    {
      "content": "事实证明当你",
      "from": 223.44,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 74,
      "to": 225.29
    },
    {
      "content": "选择专辑时有一件事对你很有帮助",
      "from": 225.29,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 75,
      "to": 229.74
    },
    {
      "content": "作为开发者是",
      "from": 229.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 76,
      "to": 230.7
    },
    {
      "content": "如果你对不同大语言模型的智能或能力有良好直觉",
      "from": 230.7,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 77,
      "to": 236.0
    },
    {
      "content": "你可以尝试大量模型并看哪个效果最好",
      "from": 236.0,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 78,
      "to": 238.94
    },
    {
      "content": "但随着使用不同模型",
      "from": 238.94,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 79,
      "to": 240.86
    },
    {
      "content": "我开始形成哪些模型适合何种任务的直觉",
      "from": 240.86,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 80,
      "to": 245.47
    },
    {
      "content": "并保持这些直觉",
      "from": 245.47,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 81,
      "to": 246.83
    },
    {
      "content": "在编写有效问题时也会更高效",
      "from": 246.83,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 82,
      "to": 250.73
    },
    {
      "content": "以及为任务选择合适模型",
      "from": 250.73,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 83,
      "to": 253.49
    },
    {
      "content": "我想与大家分享一些想法",
      "from": 253.49,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 84,
      "to": 255.99
    },
    {
      "content": "关于如何磨练直觉",
      "from": 255.99,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 85,
      "to": 257.87
    },
    {
      "content": "哪些模型适合你的应用",
      "from": 257.87,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 86,
      "to": 261.43
    },
    {
      "content": "让我们通过使用模型执行指令的例子说明",
      "from": 261.43,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 87,
      "to": 266.07
    },
    {
      "content": "以删除或屏蔽pii（个人身份信息）",
      "from": 266.07,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 88,
      "to": 270.8
    },
    {
      "content": "所以删除私密敏感信息",
      "from": 270.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 89,
      "to": 273.6
    },
    {
      "content": "例如使用模型总结客户通话",
      "from": 273.6,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 90,
      "to": 278.66
    },
    {
      "content": "则可能生成七月十四日的摘要",
      "from": 278.66,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 91,
      "to": 281.88
    },
    {
      "content": "第二第三条涉及杰西卡·阿尔瓦雷斯的社会安全号码及地址",
      "from": 281.88,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 92,
      "to": 286.06
    },
    {
      "content": "支持工单等信息",
      "from": 286.06,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 93,
      "to": 287.68
    },
    {
      "content": "这段文本包含大量敏感",
      "from": 287.68,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 94,
      "to": 290.22
    },
    {
      "content": "个人身份信息现在",
      "from": 290.22,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 95,
      "to": 293.38
    },
    {
      "content": "假设我们需要从此类摘要中移除所有pii",
      "from": 293.38,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 96,
      "to": 297.45
    },
    {
      "content": "因为我们需要用于下游客户分析",
      "from": 297.45,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 97,
      "to": 302.8
    },
    {
      "content": "并保护客户信息",
      "from": 302.8,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 98,
      "to": 304.24
    },
    {
      "content": "在下游分析前需先清除pii",
      "from": 304.24,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 99,
      "to": 308.51
    },
    {
      "content": "因此你可以提示模型识别以下文本中的所有pii",
      "from": 308.51,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 100,
      "to": 315.11
    },
    {
      "content": "然后返回带有删除标记的文本，包括删除冒号等",
      "from": 315.11,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 101,
      "to": 319.069
    },
    {
      "content": "事实证明，更大的前沿模型往往更能遵循指令",
      "from": 320.069,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 102,
      "to": 326.74
    },
    {
      "content": "而较小的模型则擅长回答简单事实性问题",
      "from": 326.74,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 103,
      "to": 331.459
    },
    {
      "content": "但不太擅长执行指令",
      "from": 331.459,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 104,
      "to": 334.24
    },
    {
      "content": "如果在较小模型上运行此提示",
      "from": 334.24,
      "location": 2,
      "music": 0.0,
      "sid": 105,
      "to": 336.6
    },
    {
      "content": "使用八亿参数的开源llama3.1模型",
